<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<HR ALIGN="center" SIZE="1">
<font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="-1"> 
<h3><center>THE MASKS FOR THE GROUPS</center></h3>
<h4><center><a href="group.html.de">deutsche version</a></center></h4>
<HR ALIGN="center" SIZE="1">
<OL>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>name</STRONG>:&nbsp;name a group, e.g. 'kein mensch ist illegal'.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>email</STRONG>:&nbsp;e-mail of the group. If given, it will always be published.&nbsp;<EM>optional</EM>.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>homepage</STRONG>:&nbsp;homepage of the group. If given, it will always be published.&nbsp;<EM>optional</EM>.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>adresse</STRONG>:&nbsp;postal adress of the group. If given, it will always be published.&nbsp;<EM>optional</EM>.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>telefon</STRONG>:&nbsp;telephone number of the group. If given, it will always be published.&nbsp;<EM>optional</EM>.
	<BR><BR>
</OL>


</body>
</html>